text.tspan: A researcher conducted an experiment to examine whether amino acid uptake by in vitro

tspan.tspan: It is almost certain that mean amino acid uptake depends on NaCN. There

text.tspan: is also extremenly strong evidence that it is different for different fish
Intestinal preparations from fish was affected by NaCN (sodium cyanide).
Only six such preparations could be obtained from each fish, so a randomised block
experiment was conducted with four fish being the blocks.
